description: This is just for fun to help quiz people to see how much they know about big band music and hopefully to teach a little bit. Technically, the bands included here range over both traditional jazz big bands, as well as the later jump blues bands. These are all included in the broad/sometimes a little vague at the edges 'swing era.'

Alexa ask Big band trivia to play

name: BigBandTrivia
shortDescription: Trivia about big bands, both what their signature song was (according to the band) and what they got to be known for, which weren't always the same thing.
